<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Auspicious Dates | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@600&family=Quicksand:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css">
</head>
<body>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
  <script>AOS.init({ duration: 2000, once: true });</script>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-sec-auspiciousdates">
    <div class="hero-content-auspiciousdates fade-in-up">
      <h1>Select the Auspicious Dates</h1>
      <p>Choose dates that resonate with tradition, convenience, and celebration.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section-auspiciousdates" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="text-content-auspiciousdates">
      <h2>Why Dates Matter</h2>
      <p>
        The date you choose is more than just a placeholder—it's the heartbeat of your celebration. Whether you're guided by cherished traditions, astrological significance, or simply what works best for your loved ones, selecting the perfect day brings emotional depth and joyful anticipation. A well-chosen date ensures your memories are built on harmony, convenience, and a touch of magic.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cards -->
  <section class="section-auspiciousdates" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="homecoming-cards-section-auspiciousdates">
      <div class="homecoming-card-auspiciousdates" data-aos="zoom-in">        
        <div class="homecoming-card-content-auspiciousdates">
          <h2>Season & Weather</h2>
          <p>Choose a month with favorable weather and a season that fits your mood—spring blooms or autumn warmth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="homecoming-card-auspiciousdates" data-aos="zoom-in">        
        <div class="homecoming-card-content-auspiciousdates">
          <h2>Venue Availability</h2>
          <p>Ensure your preferred venues are available and not double-booked, especially during peak seasons.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="homecoming-card-auspiciousdates" data-aos="zoom-out">        
        <div class="homecoming-card-content-auspiciousdates">
          <h2>Public Holidays</h2>
          <p>Cross-check national or religious holidays that might affect travel plans or guest availability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="homecoming-card-auspiciousdates" data-aos="zoom-in">       
        <div class="homecoming-card-content-auspiciousdates">
          <h2>Budget-Friendly Dates</h2>
          <p>Off-season dates often come with lower costs and greater flexibility for vendors and bookings.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="homecoming-card-auspiciousdates" data-aos="zoom-in">        
        <div class="homecoming-card-content-auspiciousdates">
          <h2>Astrological Timing</h2>
          <p>If tradition guides you, consult an astrologer or calendar for auspicious dates and planetary alignments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/astrologers" class="luxury-button-auspiciousdates">Meet our Astrologers</a>
    
  </section>

  
  <!-- Advice -->
  <section class="section-auspiciousdates" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="engagement-advice-box-auspiciousdates">
      <h4><i class="icon-lightbulb"></i> Fiore’s Date-Planning Advice</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>✔️ Book popular venues early if your date lands on a holiday or weekend.</li>
        <li>✔️ Check school/university schedules for students in your circle.</li>
        <li>✔️ Align with your event theme—sunset dinner or garden morning?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call-to-Action -->
  <section class="section-auspiciousdates" data-aos="fade-up" style="text-align: center;">
    <h2>Ready to Set the Date?</h2>
    <p>Lock in your timeline and move forward with planning the perfect celebration.</p>
    <a href="/homecoming_planning" class="luxury-button-auspiciousdates">Back to Planning Guide</a>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
